From ff4d8998e84dcf52ba74716ab0512217eace6734 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Sat, 8 Mar 2025 23:03:41 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: mac80211: set WMM in ML reconfiguration
Git-commit: ff4d8998e84dcf52ba74716ab0512217eace6734
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

In the per-STA profiles for added links in multi-link reconfiguration
the WMM element should be included. Fix that.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250308225541.59902f783420.I362c3101d3f523a8db37c16cd7b5f573d76a36e6@changeid
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 net/mac80211/mlme.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/net/mac80211/mlme.c b/net/mac80211/mlme.c
index 94d9d9ca42fe..bfd3653a5b84 100644
--- a/net/mac80211/mlme.c
+++ b/net/mac80211/mlme.c
@@ -10435,6 +10435,7 @@ int ieee80211_mgd_assoc_ml_reconf(struct ieee80211_sub_if_data *sdata,
 			return -ENOMEM;
 
 		data->assoc_link_id = -1;
+		data->wmm = true;
 
 		uapsd_supported = true;
 		ieee80211_ml_reconf_selectors(userspace_selectors);
-- 
2.53.0

